 ome\, the Maitlands attempt to scare them away without success. Their eff
 orts attract Beetlejuice (Michael Keaton)\, a rambunctious spirit whose h
 elp quickly becomes dangerous for the Maitlands and innocent Lydia. [92 m
 in\; comedy\, horror\; English]</p><p><strong>This screening is in conjun
 ction with IU Auditorium's upcoming April 10-12 performances of</strong><
 a class="external" href="https://www.iuauditorium.com/events/detail/beetl
 ejuice-2026"><i><strong>Beetlejuice: The Musical</strong></i></a><strong>
 .</strong></p>
