SUMMARY:Mamma Mia! | Pop Music(als)!
DESCRIPTION:Bride-to-be Sophie (Amanda Seyfried) has just one wish to mak
 e her wedding perfect: to have her father walk her down the aisle. Now sh
 e just has to figure out who he is! Join the laughter and fun of this irr
 esistibly charming musical celebration of mothers\, daughters\, fathers\,
  true loves lost\, and the romantic possibilities of what can happen on a
  magical Greek island when you throw a little (a lotta) ABBA in the mix! 
 Academy Award-winner Meryl Streep leads an all-star cast\, including Pier
 ce Brosnan\, Colin Firth\, Stellan SkarsgĂĄrd\, and Dominic Cooper. Based
  on the Broadway smash-hit and brimming with all the infectious ABBA song
 s we know and love. [108 min\; comedy\, musical\; English and Greek with 
 English subtitles]
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Bride-to-be Sophie (Amanda Seyfried) ha
 s just one wish to make her wedding perfect: to have her father walk her 
 down the aisle. Now she just has to figure out who he is! Join the laught
 er and fun of this irresistibly charming musical celebration of mothers\,
  daughters\, fathers\, true loves lost\, and the romantic possibilities o
 f what can happen on a magical Greek island when you throw a little (a lo
 tta) ABBA in the mix! Academy Award-winner Meryl Streep leads an all-star
  cast\, including Pierce Brosnan\, Colin Firth\, Stellan SkarsgĂĄrd\, and
  Dominic Cooper. Based on the Broadway smash-hit and brimming with all th
 e infectious ABBA songs we know and love. [108 min\; comedy\, musical\; E
 nglish and Greek with English subtitles]</p>
